    "Historically, spear phishing was primarily used against governments and businesses.",
    "However, with AI tools that can scrape data from various sources, spear phishing will become more common and more effective.",
    "Automated harassmentBeyond data theft and blackmail, GenAI can be used for automated harassment.",
    "Cybercriminals, as well as individuals with malicious intent, can use GenAI technology to launch harassment campaigns that result in service disruptions, ruined reputations, or more traditional forms of online harassment.",
    "Victims could range from businesses to private individuals or public figures."
